query:
SELECT 
  CASE 
    WHEN partNumber IN ('959993-902', '959757-902', '821125-936', '959961-302', '821725-901', '959941-902', '880952-704', '880952-706', '880952-705') THEN 'Crawler Delivery'
    ELSE 'Existing DB'
  END as source,
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN description IS NOT NULL AND LENGTH(description) > 100 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_description,
  AVG(LENGTH(description)) as avg_desc_length
FROM products 
WHERE brand = 'Agilent'
GROUP BY source
